{"tid":266864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"翡翠台 不存在，要刪除嗎？","createTime":"2017-06-01T21:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T21:37:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f61b8f515e1a76e0948f836ea2a52bc0ef10aabe","tid":266864,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T21:06:35.000Z","msg":"【陸續正常番！】無綫81台「翡翠台」一度消失 多區《射鵰》迷嬲爆<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170601&amp;guid=56771175&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170601%26guid%3D56771175%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=Lz%2FlKVMzjY173D09amOymTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=2e98853c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170601%26guid%3D56771175%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=35c8334b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170601&amp;guid=56771175&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n即時突發  2017-06-01 21:00:40 HKT\t <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170601/large/1496322645_9545.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170601%2Flarge%2F1496322645_9545.jpg&h=0503fdc7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【22:36 更新】無綫81台「翡翠台」已陸續回復正常。<br />\n<br />\n無綫81台「翡翠台」無訊號？《蘋果》晚上收到多區讀者報料，聲稱無綫81台「翡翠台」突然中斷訊號，正在欣賞《射鵰英雄傳》的巿民，卻發現電視機畫面突然變黑，只出現「無訊號」或「無服務」等。<br />\n<br />\n受影響的巿民分別位於西環、香港仔、葵青、黃大仙、深水埗、長沙灣及屯門等，其中居於長沙灣的余先生更發現「81台離奇消失」，他發現畫面沒有無訊號後，曾嘗試轉台，卻發現「由77台一跳就跳到82台」，感到十分不滿。<br />\n<br />\n居於葵青區私樓的李先生，今晚8時許正收看翡翠台《射鵰》劇集，但突然電視機沒有聲響，他看到畫面出現「翡翠台 不存在，要刪除嗎？」字句，以為大廈天線有問題，但查看後發現其他台訊卻正常。此時走廊亦傳來鄰居議論聲，大約5分鐘後涉事電視台頻道回復正常。李先生不滿說：「平時都好少睇無綫，估唔到間中睇下都有事，作為大台唔應該咁囉！」<br />\n<br />\n⁠⁠⁠⁠⁠據知，無綫81台晚上離奇消失事件，因機器故障，觀眾未能接收該台。其後，後備系統已隨即啟動，服務於1分19秒後恢復正常。有受影響巿民向《蘋果》表示，事後立即致電無綫客戶服務熱線，職員著他「熄機，再重新開機，然後追過個台就得」，雖然已回復正常，但他不滿對方沒有就事件致歉。"},{"pid":"6f6f1d3f361b484283a89a4535f5895884b69fd0","tid":266864,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T21:21:34.000Z","msg":"不滿對方沒有就事件致歉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗唔洗同你道歉呀？<br />\n港豬嚟"},{"pid":"f56c4d7fd775a8756fe12a5dfcae23854bae297b","tid":266864,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T21:37:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不滿對方沒有就事件致歉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗唔洗同你道歉呀？<br />\n港豬嚟</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}